ActPublic Service Employment Act
PrecisAppointment of EDITH CLOUTIER, C.M., C.Q., of Val-d'Or, Quebec, as a special adviser to the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development, to serve as a Member of the Interim Board for the establishment of the National Council for Reconciliation, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term of six months, effective December 11, 2017.
